<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs - Negotix</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/faq.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- CSS moved to faq.css -->
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <div class="background-shapes">
        <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-4"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-5"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-6"></div>
    </div>

<div class="faq-content">
    <!-- FAQ Header -->
    <header class="faq-header">
        <h1>FAQs</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- FAQ Content -->
    <main>
        <section class="faq-section">
            <h2>Orders</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I know if my order has been confirmed?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Your order is confirmed when you see the confirmation message on screen after checkout. Currently, we do not send email confirmations for orders.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I modify or cancel my order?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, cancelling your order is possible. If you cancel, the second highest bidder will automatically win the auction.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Oh no! I made a mistake with the bidding details in my order. How can I make changes or tell the seller?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Please contact us directly through our Contact page and we'll assist you with any changes needed.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq-section">
            <h2>Delivery</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What are your delivery options, pricing, and cut-off timings?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We offer two delivery options: home delivery and office delivery. Home delivery is available for residential addresses, while office delivery is optimized for business locations with reception services. Both options have standard and express shipping speeds available.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>I didn't get my delivery! It's late! What's going on?</h3>
                        <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Contact our customer support team immediately for assistance with delayed deliveries.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>

<%- include('./partials/footer') %>

<a href="#" class="back-to-top" id="backToTop">
    <i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i>
</a>

<canvas id="particles"></canvas>



<script src="/js/faq.js"></script>
</body>
</html>